<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">

    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 220, alt: "Profile Image" %>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>I am a software developer passionate about solving day to day problems using technology thereby having an
          improved state of life. I am a lifelong learner always excited about learning new stuff.</p>
        <p>I love using my knowledge to build awesome products and tools which would benefit people of all ages and
          different interests with the aim of transforming lives for the better.</p>
        <p>I endeavour to always deliver my work on time, on budget while having constant communication with a client to
          ensure delivery of the right product that is according to the client's specifications.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobHistory">
            Job History
          </button>

          &nbsp; &nbsp;

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#eduBackground"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="eduBackground">
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-body" style="width: 100%">
              Andela Kenya - From December 2017
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>

        <p>
        <div class="collapse" id="eduBackground">
          <div class="card card-block" style="width: 100%">
            Multimedia University of Kenya - From September 2015
          </div>
        </div>
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
